&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you an experienced Mental Health Nurse with a solid background in Dementia?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you looking for the next step in your career?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If so then this could be the job for you…………&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Band 6 Mental Health Nurse - &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;30 hrs per week - North West Sussex Dementia Assessment Service&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The North West Sussex Dementia Assessment Service provides diagnostic assessment and post diagnostic interventions for people with suspected dementia within the Horsham/Crawley and Mid Sussex localities. It works in partnership with the Alzheimer’s Society.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Early diagnosis is a fundamental component of the National Dementia Strategy and aims to empower people and their carers to make decisions about their future based on early diagnostic information relating to their condition&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Dementia Assessment service has gained accreditation with the Royal College of Psychiatrists&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a hardworking and highly organised mental health nurse. You will need to be a skilled communicator both written and oral and have a passion for working in the field of dementia.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;In return for your skills and expertise we can offer you a variety of rewarding challenges, continued training and development and the opportunity to work within a friendly welcoming and supportive team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This post offers a Golden Hello, or a Relocation package up to a maximum of £2000. (pro rata applies and subject to terms and conditions. Please see attached Protocol document).&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;For further information please contact: David Shattock, Team Leader on 03003040026&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameDavid ShattockJob titleTeam LeaderEmail addressdavid.shattock@sussexpartnership.nhs.ukTelephone number03003040026&lt;/p&gt;
